aVOne of the Acumen Fund fellows at my organization,
p217
aVSuraj Sudhakar,
p218
aVhas what we call moral imagination \u2014
p219
aVthe ability to put yourself in another person's shoes
p220
aVand lead from that perspective.
p221
aVAnd he's been working with this young group of men
p222
aVwho come from the largest slum in the world, Kibera.
p223
aVAnd they're incredible guys.
p224
aVAnd together they started a book club
