aa(lp230
VAnd I have learned so much
p231
aVfrom Chris and Kevin
p232
aVand Alex and Herbert
p233
aVand all of these young men.
p234
aVAlex, in some ways, said it best.
p235
aVHe said, "We used to feel like nobodies,
p236
aVbut now we feel like somebodies."
p237
aVAnd I think we have it all wrong
p238
aVwhen we think that income is the link.
